        <strong>We're Serious about MMS!</strong>

        <p>
            MMS - A new form of messaging that lets media do the talking! Customers can enrich their messaging experience 
            with images, sounds, voice memos, and up to 1000 characters of text. MMS on the Verizon Wireless network is 
            fast, affordable and easy to use.
        </p>
		MMS features include:
        <ul>
            <li>Available throughout Verizon Wireless Enhanced Services Rate and Coverage Area with fast speeds using our High Speed EVDO data network.</li>
            <li>Send video messages that are up to 30 seconds long.</li>
            <li>Send to any Verizon Wireless Phone using the 10 digit mobile number or to any valid E-Mail address.</li>
            <li>There are six ways for a consumer to send an MMS message:
            <ul>
            	<li>Verizon Wireless phone to any Verizon Wireless phone</li> 
				<li>Verizon Wireless phone to wireless phones from other select service providers <A href="http://support.vzw.com/faqs/Picture%20Messaging/faq_pixmessaging.html#item8" class="a" target="_blank">view provider list</A></li>
				<li>Phone to any valid E-Mail Address</li>
				<li>E-Mail to Phone using Mobile Number @vzwpix.com</li> 
				<li>Phone to the on-line multimedia library - Picture &amp; Video Messaging portal</li> 
				<li>On-line multimedia composer (Picture &amp; Video Messaging portal) to any Verizon Wireless phone</li>            
            </ul>
        </ul>
        <p>
			Verizon Wireless MMS takes on a whole new face. With Animated Messaging, you can express your message with an animated character and send to any Verizon Wireless customer.        
        </p>
